# VFX2022 HW1 HDR(High dynamic range image)

## Usage
Source code is locate at code/hw1.ipynb. You can use jupyter notebook to execute my code.
If you don't want to use Jupyter, I also provide python script.
```
cd code 
python hw1.py
```

## Dependency and Environment
python 3.7.11
numpy==1.21.5
opencv-contrib-python==4.5.5.64
opencv-python==4.5.5.64
matplotlib==3.5.1
